 command, and made internal improvements: 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12027] Plugin StreamReader: fuse the iterator after an error
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12014] Add Goodbye message

to ensure plugins exit when they are no longer needed
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11972] Rename spans in the serialized form of Value
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11929] Print stderr streams to stderr in 
``pipeline_data::print_if_stream()``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11928] Add 
``tee``
 command for operating on copies of streams
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11911] Bidirectional communication and streams for plugins
fdncred 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12022] removed old 
``mv``
 command in favor of 
``umv``
 (renamed to mv)
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11993] bumped reedline

to test ExecuteHostCommand changes
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11991] added an 
``is-not-empty``
 command as a QOL improvement
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11954] allowed current day to be highlighted
WindSoilder made lots of improvements to globbing: 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12018] deprecated 
``str escape-glob``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11992] Glob: don't allow implicit casting between glob and string
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11946] Don't expand globs if user pass variables.
PanGan21 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12012] fixed: 
``to md``
 command to process empty headers
IanManske 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12010] disabled flaky network tests
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12001] added an 
``upsert``
 example
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11949] moved 
``typos``
 config to repo root
ZzMzaw 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12008] extended the clear command so it can clear the terminal's history
hustcer 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12007] made coreutils umkdir the default mkdir
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11986] fixed Windows msvc 
*.msi builds
kik4444 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12005] fixed 
``touch``
 to allow changing timestamps on directories
FilipAndersson245 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12000] replaced the Criterion benchmarking framework with Divan
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11998] made benchmark changes
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11994] fixed tests.
ayax79 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11987] fixed up an issue with dataframes
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11953] handled more errors in the REPL so they don't propagate up and kill the REPL
nils-degroot 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11952] added date support in 
``from xlsx``
sholderbach 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11947] removed some unnecessary static 
``Vec``
s
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11939] fixed 
``cargo b -p nu-command --tests``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11863] fixed a future lint by 
``truncate(false)``
 in 
``touch``
132ikl 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11921] fixed completions for directories with hidden files
Olilin1 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12035] fixed string_to_table in ssv.rs so it now filters comments. (issue #11997)
zhiburt 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11905] improved 
``table -a``
astral-l 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11902] added a --signed flag for binary into int conversions
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11854] added binary data handling to 
``bits``
 commands
ysthakur 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11849] added a ConfigDirNotFound error
