``is-not-empty``
 command as a QOL improvement
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11954] allowed current day to be highlighted
WindSoilder made lots of improvements to globbing: 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12018] deprecated 
